*libdv-1.0.0-r3 (16 Aug 2013)

  16 Aug 2013; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org> +libdv-1.0.0-r3.ebuild:
  Convert to multilib. Stack it for medialibs r13. Remove debug useflag that
  only adds -g to cflags. Drop sdl and xv useflags that did nothing since we
  dropped the gtk1 interface.

